{"tid":765530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貨尾加價 發展商無懼空置稅】將軍澳兩新盤加價推貨尾 最高加幅達8.5%","createTime":"2018-08-03T00:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T10:49:17.000Z","uid":4361,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d243538eed3477a74e7e06ae5abf256449642ae0","tid":765530,"uid":4361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:24:32.000Z","msg":"發展商無懼空置稅，繼續加價推貨尾。將軍澳日出康城兩個新盤，新地（016）旗下晉海II將部分貨尾加價8.5%，如5B座7樓F室，實用343方呎1房戶，最新定價765萬元，較3月時舊定價705.1萬元，調高59.9萬元或8.5%。該盤將於本周日（5日）推售35伙。<br />\n<br />\n另外毗鄰的會德豐（020）Malibu亦更新8號價單，將部分貨尾加價高達6.6%，如1A座12樓C室，實用459方呎，早前的定價為1016.7萬元，其後加價約6.6%至1084.3萬元，最新呎價為23623元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180802/58516871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58516871&d=BjdueF2Fu17egHyAgZSgi9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=de3467b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58516871&h=b44f80b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180802/58516871</a>"},{"pid":"a2b96dd61d19a89621eece29b61d73a9b3af1635","tid":765530,"uid":10101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"加價到無人賣先會停，當然試下水溫，睇下有無傻仔上釣"},{"pid":"f6df06eeb6bf98ed73d764f12186ef11f5f23b51","tid":765530,"uid":10101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2b96dd61d19a89621eece29b61d73a9b3af1635","tid":765530,"uid":10101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:57:35.000Z","msg":"加價到無人賣先會停，當然試下水溫，睇下有無傻仔上釣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T00:57:45.000Z","msg":"買"},{"pid":"3f7784a4d44b867d9a78bfcef8ecef0237bd994b","tid":765530,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T01:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707bf